1. *On se dugo razmišljao* (He thought for a long time). 
2. *Razmišljala* je o tome kako da postigne svoj cilj (She was thinking about how to achieve her goal). 
3. *Razmišljajući* o tome kako da pobegne, on je odlučio da pokuša da se spase (Thinking about how to escape, he decided to try to save himself). 
4. *Razmišljao* je o tome da li treba da napusti zemlju (He thought about whether he should leave the country). 
5. *Razmišljali* su o tome šta će sledeće da urade (They were thinking about what to do next). 
6. *Razmišljanja* su mu se vrtela u glavi (His thoughts were spinning in his head).